jump’INto the WEEKEND
>>the next FRONTIER
#metaEstates_VILLA {link in BIO}
future:FASHION/retail/realEstate
.
WHAT IF …. ?
// what if .. we could construct fabled beautiful worlds and environments // what if.. we could get better efficiencies through advanced technology // what if .. we could achieve building methodologies that we cant IRL // what if .. we could weave in and out of these interoperable worlds to connect with loved ones when distance and circumstances don’t allow us // what if … we could DO things in these worlds we cannot IRL // what if .. we could be anything and anyone in these worlds without being judged // what if .. we could stitch these digital experiences with the real world and all together build a BETTER ONE // what if … these digital worlds didn’t replace our incredible earth but instead enhanced it and aided with sustainability efforts to preserve it // ??? 
WHAT IF ... to infinity and beyond 
.
asking questions around the DESIGN, functionality & UTILITY of the metaVERSE and the ‘what ifs’ that it could enable us to achieve
.
metaEstates_VILLA:
a monumental complex of unbuildable SCALE , fabricated and reimagined LANDSCAPEs, a place that reconsiders SPATIAL scripting and what we can do in them, a world that is visually familiar yet challenges the laws of physics, materiality and nature. a digital space that is immersive, interactive and interoperable; readily prepared to drop into most metaverse platforms where you can EXPERIENCE a ‘world’ like no other, a world you can own: your own monumental METAVERSE abode
.
@metaestates_lab |
#luisfern5 + @the_line_visualization
#metaversearchitecture #modernarchitecture
